item.title: For the Record #232: Chime Oblivion's Self-Titled Debut
item.description: The Osees' John Dwyer and prolific new wave drummer David Barbarossa join forces in a new supergroup, Chime Oblivion, delivering 12 songs of dense, anarchic, delightful proto-punk. We discuss their self-titled debut on episode #232 "For the Record." Feed: https://fortherecordpodcast.com/podcasts/feed.xml
